songs.title: Best Around*
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
...Parties
Opps come around
We gun 'em down
It's No Limit gang
We the best around
Fuck the rest around
Choppa buck the rest around
AR with her titties out
Shut the city down
[?] from Max put it on a spliff and make it growl
[?] it's mandatory if there's guns around
Touring coast to coast city to city surfing crowds
I only do a show if there's 100k funds around
Take you to the car lot, no Range Rover
Take you to the real estate, no crib the gang go
It's the same gang gang no I will not change, oh
They ain't switching lanes 'till the game game over

[Chorus]
Pull them racks out (Pull them racks out)
Pull them straps out (Pull them straps out)
You the man now? He a man now
You the man now? He a man now
Pull them racks out (Pull them racks out)
Pull them straps out (Pull them straps out)
You the man now? He a man now
I'm the man now, yeah

[Verse 2]
I got what I got cause I worked for it
I don't gotta answer to nobody
Better have some manners cause I'm somebody
If you niggas couldn't tell I do not give a fuck
If you ain't tryna wish me well you can go to hell
[?] to bitches too, must be Jezebel
I done did this by myself I don't need no help
[?] have they back turned, I don't need you here
Say you wanna kill me
